				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>PPC also known as Pay Per Click Marketing is a quick and easy way to advertise your site on Google, Bing and Yahoo. When a potential customer goes onto Google and searches, if what they search for is a product or service that you sell, your advert will be shown on the first page search results. This means that your ads will only be shown to people who are actually interested in what you offer.</p><p>You place a bid for a particular ad spot on Google, which is based on a keyword that relates to your business. More popular keywords require higher bids to secure the spot. Once successful, the ad will then be shown every time a visitor searches for your chosen keyword. Since you only pay when a customer clicks your advert and visits your website, it’s a very cost-effective way to advertise on the internet.</p>								</div>
